OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FA farming partnership in Surrey has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #30,000 after
OL,8,Ffive hay bales crushed a young dad,
OL,9,Fseriously injuring him.
OL,11,FChristopher Rolfe, from Horsham,
OL,12,Fsustained four rib fractures when the
OL,13,Fbales fell on him at Polesden Lacey
OL,14,FFarm in April 2022.
OL,16,FEach bale was estimated to weigh 600
OL,17,Fkg and Christopher lay trapped
OL,18,Fscreaming for help until a nearby dog
OL,19,Fwalker heard his cries and called for
OL,20,Fhelp. He suffered fractures to his
OL,21,Fpelvis and ankle, as well as his ribs.
