OL,6,FHe was then airlifted to hospital,
OL,7,Fwhere he underwent emergency surgery
OL,8,Fbefore starting months of
OL,9,Frehabilitation in order to regain his
OL,10,Fmobility to start walking again and
OL,11,Fcaring for his then four-year-old son.
OL,13,FChris who was 26 at the time of the
OL,14,Fincident has now returned to farming,
OL,15,Fbut is acutely aware that he was
OL,16,Fextremely lucky.
