OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FHe said: "I was a stereotypical young
OL,7,Fman in agriculture. I always thought
OL,8,FI'd be fine ` as long as I got to
OL,9,Fdrive a quarter of a million pound
OL,10,Ftractor down the road with everyone
OL,11,Flooking at me.
OL,13,F"Now that's the last thing on my mind.
OL,14,FI very much look at every piece of
OL,15,Fmachinery in front of me and think how
OL,16,Fquickly can that thing kill me.
OL,18,F"I was lucky to come away with just a
OL,19,Fbroken hip and leg fractures. I was
OL,20,Flater told that if I had gone by road
OL,21,Fto the hospital I would have died."
