OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigation found the poorly
OL,8,Fconstructed stack of bales had not
OL,9,Fbeen stacked on firm, dry, level,
OL,10,Ffreely draining ground. Instead, they
OL,11,Fwere on top of old pallets as the barn
OL,12,Ffloor was uneven and prone to
OL,13,Fwaterlogging.
