OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FThe bales were placed in vertical
OL,7,Fcolumns and were not 'tied in' by
OL,8,Falternating the layers so the bales
OL,9,Foverlap and stop the stack from
OL,10,Fsplitting. The company had also failed
OL,11,Fto identify safe working methods for
OL,12,Funstacking bales, keeping the face
OL,13,Fracked back as bales were removed.
