OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FF Conisbee and Sons Ltd, of Ockham
OL,7,FRoad South, East Horsley, Surrey,
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Regulation
OL,9,F10 (4) of the Work at Height
OL,10,FRegulations 2005. The company was
OL,11,Ffined #36,000 and ordered to pay
OL,12,F#4,986 in costs at Staines
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on 15 May 2024.
