OL,3,CFarm fined after dad seriously injured
OL,4,Cwhen five hay bales fell on him
OL,6,FHSE inspector Sally Parkes said: "This
OL,7,Faccident would have been easily
OL,8,Favoided if the farm had followed the
OL,9,Fguidance published by either HSE or
OL,10,Fthe National Farmers Union on the safe
OL,11,Fstacking of bales. Stacking bales
OL,12,Frequires skill and should be overseen
OL,13,Fdirectly by someone with knowledge of
OL,14,Fthe industry guidance.
OL,16,F"Health and safety is a fundamental
OL,17,Frequirement of a sustainable farming
OL,18,Fbusiness yet over the last 10 years,
OL,19,Falmost one person a week is killed and
OL,20,Fmany more are seriously injured as a
OL,21,Fresult of agricultural work.
